msgstr "Bypassa o preferisci DLL Windows specifiche"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:11
msgid "Enabled (Enforce)"
msgstr "Abilitato (Imponi)"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:15
msgid "Disables Next-Gen Geometry (NGG). Fixes crashes in older Vulkan games."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita Next-Gen Geometry (NGG). Corregge crash in giochi Vulkan più "
"vecchi."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:16
msgid "Disables internal application binary interface caching."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita la cache interna dell'interfaccia binaria dell'applicazione."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:17
msgid "Disables background shader compilation."
msgstr "Disabilita la compilazione shader in background."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:18
msgid ""
"Disables Delta Color Compression. Can fix specific rendering artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita la compressione del colore Delta. Può risolvere artefatti di "
"rendering specifici."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:19
msgid ""
"Disables Variable Rate Shading (VRS). Fixes UI artifacts in some games."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita Variable Rate Shading (VRS). Corregge artefatti UI in alcuni "
"giochi."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:20
msgid ""
"Disables Graphics Pipeline Library (GPL) to troubleshoot startup crashes."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita Graphics Pipeline Library (GPL) per risolvere crash all'avvio."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:21
msgid "Forces fallback command submission mode. Helps diagnosing GPU hangs."
msgstr ""
"Forza la modalità di invio comandi di fallback. Aiuta a diagnosticare "
"blocchi GPU."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:22
msgid "Disables Vertex Runtime Shading. Can fix specific rendering artifacts."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita Vertex Runtime Shading. Può risolvere artefatti di rendering "
"specifici."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:23
msgid ""
"Precompiles shaders during loading screens to reduce in-game stuttering."
msgstr ""
"Precompila gli shader durante le schermate di caricamento per ridurre i "
"rallentamenti in-game."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:24
msgid ""
"Disables AMD Texture Compression. Fixes texture glitches on APUs and Steam "
"Deck."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita la compressione texture AMD. Corregge problemi di texture su APU "
"e Steam Deck."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:27
msgid "AMD RADV Debug Options"
msgstr "Opzioni di debug AMD RADV"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:28
msgid "Fine-tune AMD Radeon Vulkan driver behavior"
msgstr "Ottimizza il comportamento del driver Vulkan AMD Radeon"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:29
msgid "Enable RADV Debug"
msgstr "Abilita debug RADV"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-debug.vala:30
msgid "Apply low-level driver bugfixes and overrides"
msgstr "Applica correzioni e override del driver di basso livello"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:15
msgid "Enables experimental hardware Ray Tracing support."
msgstr "Abilita il supporto sperimentale per il Ray Tracing hardware."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:16
msgid "Optimizes Smart Access Memory / Resizable BAR utilization."
msgstr "Ottimizza l'utilizzo di Smart Access Memory / Resizable BAR."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:17
msgid "Enables Next-Gen Geometry Culling for better geometry performance."
msgstr ""
"Abilita Next-Gen Geometry Culling per migliori prestazioni geometriche."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:18
msgid "Graphics Pipeline Library. Drastically reduces shader stuttering."
msgstr ""
"Graphics Pipeline Library. Riduce drasticamente i rallentamenti degli "
"shader."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:19
msgid ""
"Enables User Space Queue submission. Can improve CPU-bound game performance "
"on modern kernels."
msgstr ""
"Abilita l'invio di code nello spazio utente. Può migliorare le prestazioni "
"dei giochi limitati dalla CPU su kernel moderni."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:20
msgid ""
"Emulates hardware Ray Tracing using software compute shaders on AMD GPUs. "
"Enables RT features on unsupported hardware at the cost of a drastic "
"performance drop."
msgstr ""
"Emula il Ray Tracing hardware usando shader di calcolo software su GPU AMD. "
"Abilita le funzionalità RT su hardware non supportato al costo di un "
"drastico calo delle prestazioni."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:23
msgid "AMD RADV Performance Tests"
msgstr "Test di prestazione AMD RADV"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:24
msgid "Enable experimental AMD performance features"
msgstr "Abilita funzionalità sperimentali di prestazione AMD"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:25
msgid "Enable RADV Perftest"
msgstr "Abilita RADV Perftest"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-radv-perf-test.vala:26
msgid "Test bleeding-edge driver optimizations (use with caution)"
msgstr "Testa ottimizzazioni all'avanguardia del driver (usare con cautela)"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-resolution-field.vala:37
msgid "Auto detect"
msgstr "Rilevamento automatico"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-resolution-field.vala:38
#: src/widgets/mangohud/mangohud-presets-page.vala:26
#: src/widgets/mangohud/mangohud-presets-page.vala:54
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Personalizzato"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-resolution-field.vala:69
#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-spin-tile.vala:44
msgid "Set"
msgstr "Imposta"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-resolution-field.vala:70
msgid "Apply the custom resolution"
msgstr "Applica la risoluzione personalizzata"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-spin-tile.vala:45
msgid "Apply the FPS value"
msgstr "Applica il valore FPS"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:30
msgid ""
"Enables VKD3D's internal shader cache on disk. Drastically reduces micro-"
"stuttering and speeds up consecutive loading times."
msgstr ""
"Abilita la cache shard interna di VKD3D su disco. Riduce drasticamente i "
"micro-rallentamenti e accelera i tempi di caricamento consecutivi."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:31
msgid ""
"Forces VKD3D to use system RAM instead of VRAM for caching shader "
"compilation data, ensuring smoother data stream between CPU and GPU."
msgstr ""
"Forza VKD3D a utilizzare la RAM di sistema invece della VRAM per la cache "
"dei dati di compilazione degli shader, garantendo un flusso di dati più "
"fluido tra CPU e GPU."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:32
msgid ""
"Uses host-visible VRAM for staging buffers. Drastically reduces stuttering "
"if Resizable BAR / SAM is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Utilizza VRAM visibile all'host per i buffer staging. Riduce drasticamente i"
" rallentamenti se Resizable BAR / SAM è abilitato."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:33
msgid ""
"Disables host-visible VRAM staging buffers. Use as a compatibility fallback "
"if experiencing memory-related crashes."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita i buffer staging VRAM visibili all'host. Utilizza come ripiego di"
" compatibilità in caso di crash legati alla memoria."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:34
msgid ""
"Disables D3D12 Ray Tracing (DXR) capabilities entirely. Significantly "
"improves performance and stability on GPUs without strong hardware RT "
"support."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita completamente le capacità di Ray Tracing D3D12 (DXR). Migliora "
"significativamente prestazioni e stabilità su GPU senza un forte supporto RT"
" hardware."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:35
msgid ""
"Exposes D3D12 Ray Tracing (DXR 1.1 and 1.0) capabilities to the game via "
"Vulkan extensions."
msgstr ""
"Espone le capacità di Ray Tracing D3D12 (DXR 1.1 e 1.0) al gioco tramite "
"estensioni Vulkan."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:36
msgid ""
"Restricts Ray Tracing capabilities to DXR 1.0 only. Useful for older RT "
"games that crash with DXR 1.1."
msgstr ""
"Limita le capacità di Ray Tracing alla sola DXR 1.0. Utile per giochi RT più"
" vecchi che crashano con DXR 1.1."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:37
msgid ""
"Forces Ray Tracing BVH acceleration structures to be built on the CPU "
"instead of the GPU. Severe performance impact!"
msgstr ""
"Forza la costruzione delle strutture di accelerazione BVH del Ray Tracing "
"sulla CPU invece che sulla GPU. Impatto severo sulle prestazioni!"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:38
msgid ""
"Aggressively unifies memory allocators for textures and buffers to save a "
"small amount of VRAM."
msgstr ""
"Unifica aggressivamente gli allocatori di memoria per texture e buffer per "
"risparmiare una piccola quantità di VRAM."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:39
msgid ""
"Enables advanced GPU Virtual Addressing to improve Direct3D 12 memory "
"mapping in massive open-world games."
msgstr ""
"Abilita l'indirizzamento virtuale GPU avanzato per migliorare il mapping "
"della memoria Direct3D 12 nei giochi open-world massivi."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:40
msgid ""
"Disables descriptor caches. Workaround for specific games suffering from "
"memory leaks."
msgstr ""
"Disabilita le cache dei descrittori. Soluzione alternativa per giochi "
"specifici che soffrono di memory leak."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:41
msgid ""
"Forces the GPU to maintain stable clock rates. Intended for accurate "
"benchmarking only."
msgstr ""
"Forza la GPU a mantenere frequenze di clock stabili. Inteso solo per "
"benchmarking accurato."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:42
msgid ""
"Alters how root parameters are passed to compute shaders. Can fix specific "
"rendering glitches."
msgstr ""
"Modifica il modo in cui i parametri root vengono passati agli shader di "
"calcolo. Può risolvere problemi di rendering specifici."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:43
msgid ""
"Allows unaligned stencil buffer clears. Workaround for certain older "
"Direct3D 12 renderers."
msgstr ""
"Consente la cancellazione non allineata del buffer stencil. Soluzione "
"alternativa per alcuni renderer Direct3D 12 più vecchi."

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:46
msgid "VKD3D Proton Configurations"
msgstr "Configurazioni VKD3D Proton"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:48
msgid "Enable VKD3D Option"
msgstr "Abilita opzione VKD3D"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-config.vala:49
msgid "Test specific Direct3D 12 compatibility workarounds and optimizations"
msgstr ""
"Testa soluzioni di compatibilità e ottimizzazioni specifiche per Direct3D 12"

#: src/widgets/games/launch-options-editor/launch-options-editor-vkd3d-log-level.vala:22
msgid "Adjust how much debugging information VKD3D prints to the terminal."
msgstr ""
"Regola la quantità di informazioni di debug che VKD3D stampa nel terminale."

